{"tid":490930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡頓保：因為摩連奴我先唔吹英超！","createTime":"2017-12-06T05:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T16:24:02.000Z","uid":107405,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"1e90106dc7a36573c56870f7dc5fb6f0e9a50ae0","tid":490930,"uid":107405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:03:35.000Z","msg":"卡頓保在2月時宣佈不再擔當英超球證，轉到沙地阿拉伯繼續執法。<br />\n42歲的卡頓保自2004年起成為英超球證，在2017年1月執吹完曼聯對史篤城一仗後就決定離開。<br />\n那場比賽朗尼打破了卜比查爾頓在曼聯的入球紀錄，最終兩隊打成1：1平手。<br />\n卡頓保透露賽後摩連奴闖進更衣室，向他發炮指他漏判曼聯一球12碼表示不滿。<br />\n「史篤城的球場十分寒冷，而執法曼聯的賽事永遠都不易，我覺得自己做得很好，但摩連奴突然闖入我的更衣室向我發炮 ，指我看不到史篤城球員有手球，不斷指責我，但我肯定我沒有做錯。<br />\n「回家途中我在想是否犯了錯，我老婆都知我的態度開始有點轉變，我亦問自己是否適合再做英超裁判，經一輪反省後，我發現已不再享受，所以選擇離開。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Wq1B2vxQIxiLuW1rWFbBr9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=7a605c7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"47cdcb37c3d6ce6d90ab3b453356ae3d47fe05ae","tid":490930,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:06:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e130e0313d2c0e2876142f5ddcf9ba250ffbaf","tid":490930,"uid":136430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:06:32.000Z","msg":"Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e1f2c2950d63f7d6e2aa6b2517e03dfb39e6914","tid":490930,"uid":8883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:06:51.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"fa293738b96f3d6f390978572eb26d49bd0e2a8f","tid":490930,"uid":141421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:08:11.000Z","msg":"摩佬好波"},{"pid":"4e514f5fc8a92902bc9e6a175d505f8bfd8bde60","tid":490930,"uid":70028,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T05:17:19.000Z","msg":"球證衰過黑警，永遠唔認錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\